mt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22175701/Favero-Assioma-DUO-Shi-Shimano-SPD-SL-compatible-road-power-meter-pedal-spindle-kit-detail-1068x300.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22175701/Favero-Assioma-DUO-Shi-Shimano-SPD-SL-compatible-road-power-meter-pedal-spindle-kit-detail-1493x420.jpg 1493w\"></a></p><p>The single Favero Assioma DUO-Shi power meter pedal kit is compatible with all Ultegra R8000/R6800, 105 R7000, Tiagra R550/R540 SPD-SL pedals.</p><p>The made-in-Italy Assioma DUO-Shi kit sells for 690€ (including VAT), is IP67 rated waterproof, and includes a 2-year warranty. The new power meter pedal kit is available now, and ships within a week, so you’ll be swapping out your Shimano axles for power sensors in no time!</p><p><a href=\"https://cycling.favero.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>cycling.Favero.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ca46a988360ab64e06e4bb83c43d0e1d991034d2d348f21a3749bcb52b6e2504","category":"Cycling"}